                (as low as a few dollars per month) and your ESP costs. There are
                no per-profile fees, no volume limits, and no feature gates.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">
                Can Notifuse replace Klaviyo?
