                Both platforms offer REST APIs with OpenAPI specifications.
                Notifuse adds a built-in SMTP relay for legacy system
                integration. Klaviyo uses the JSON:API specification and provides
                SDKs in Python, PHP, Ruby, and Node.js. Notifuse focuses on a
                clean REST API without SDKs.
              </p>
            </div>

